  "Say": {
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "Kanna! How's the new world treating you? You're looking a little...out of sorts. Have you not been eating your vegetables? How do you expect to rescue Princess Sakuno and defeat Oda Nobunaga if you don't eat your vegetables?"
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "It's obvious that we don't have the strength to take on Nobunaga in a head-on battle. We don't even know where to find organic supplies around here. I don't think any of our soldiers are even getting five servings of vegetables. But Nobunaga's troops are so healthy. It's like they landed right on a garden or something."
      },
      "2": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "If Oda's Army can get used to this place, we can too. Are you up for a little journey? You can travel the world, regain your strength, make some powerful allies, and find out how we can set up a produce supply route!"
      },
      "illustration": {
